Package: minicom
Version: 2.00.0
Revision: 1
Depends: ncurses
BuildDepends: ncurses, gettext
Source: http://www.clinet.fi/~walker/%n-%v.src.tar.gz           
SourceDirectory: %n-%v
Patch: %f.patch
ConfigureParams: --enable-lock-dir=%p/var/run --enable-dfl-port=/dev/tty.modem --mandir=%p/share/man --infodir=%p/share/info --libexecdir=%p/lib
DocFiles: ABOUT-NLS AUTHORS COPYING ChangeLog INSTALL NEWS README
Description: Serial communication program
DescDetail: <<
Minicom is a serial communication program. It is a Unix clone of the
well-known MS-DOS Telix program. It has ANSI color, a dialing directory,
dial-a-list, and a scripting language.
<<
